### Tab 3: Scheduled Jobs

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant React as Dashboard.jsx
    participant RQ as React Query
    participant API as GET /api/dashboard/scheduled
    participant DB as msdb.dbo.sysschedules

    User->>React: Clicks "Scheduled" tab
    React->>RQ: useQuery('scheduledJobs')
    Note over RQ: enabled: activeTab === 'scheduled' ✅
    Note over RQ: staleTime: 60000ms (1 min)
    RQ->>API: GET /api/dashboard/scheduled
    API->>DB: Query sysjobschedules + sysschedules WHERE next_run > NOW
    DB-->>API: Future scheduled runs
    API-->>RQ: JSON { count, jobs[], frequencySummary }
    RQ-->>React: Render schedule table
```

**When does it fetch?**

| Trigger | Fetches? | Why |
|---------|----------|-----|
| Click the "Scheduled" tab | ✅ | `enabled` becomes `true` |
| Switch away and back within 60s | ❌ Uses cache | `staleTime: 60000` — data is "fresh" for 1 minute |
| Switch away and back after 60s | ✅ | Data is now "stale", refetches |
| Click "Refresh" button | ✅ | Calls `refetchScheduled()` manually |
| New schedule added in SQL Server | ❌ | No auto-refresh. Must click Refresh or re-open tab |
| Browser tab regains focus | ❌ | `refetchOnWindowFocus: false` |

**What SQL does it run?**

```sql
SELECT j.name, s.name AS scheduleName,
       msdb.dbo.agent_datetime(js.next_run_date, js.next_run_time) AS nextScheduledRun,
       CASE s.freq_type
           WHEN 4 THEN 'Daily'
           WHEN 8 THEN 'Weekly'
           WHEN 16 THEN 'Monthly'
           ...
       END AS frequency,
       j.enabled AS jobEnabled
FROM msdb.dbo.sysjobs j
JOIN msdb.dbo.sysjobschedules js ON ...
JOIN msdb.dbo.sysschedules s ON ...
WHERE js.next_run_date > 0
  AND agent_datetime(next_run_date, next_run_time) > GETDATE()  -- ← Only future runs
  AND EXISTS (... Db_Job_Name ...)  -- ← Only configured jobs
ORDER BY nextScheduledRun ASC
```

**What data comes back?**

```
{
  count: 8,
  frequencySummary: { "Daily": 5, "Weekly": 2, "One Time": 1 },
  jobs: [{
    jobName: "Expense_Report_Audit_Kowa",
    clientName: "Kowa",
    scheduleName: "Daily_0800_EST",
    nextScheduledRun: "2026-03-03T08:00:00",
    frequency: "Daily",
    timeUntil: "9h 20m",
    jobEnabled: true
  }]
}
```

